Information
------------------------------

Expedition Unknown Series 2 Special: A Day in the Life
Go behind the scenes with Josh Gates' crew while they film Expedition Unknown and navigate through technical logistics, practical jokes and hair-raising adventures. Also, see never-televised bonus footage from Josh's craziest experiences.
